{"tid":1923824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天花板襲警？】衝鋒車直入停車場刮天花","createTime":"2020-03-13T09:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T11:41:56.000Z","uid":209657,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"64d5d66cb93094550d585ca796824bdf02ddbb95","tid":1923824,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2531811/org/11e792ec87409ceaf0d2c4f3ae21868c.jpg/r7IlXhvDNxD8hH2lVr6Ul__aCySuTjL-KjpDFSo6QxU?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2531811%2Forg%2F11e792ec87409ceaf0d2c4f3ae21868c.jpg%2Fr7IlXhvDNxD8hH2lVr6Ul__aCySuTjL-KjpDFSo6QxU%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=f8b15e15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0fb6677dc09d08d4b6d82fee413d0eeb02c6f6c","tid":1923824,"uid":266410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"低能，唔識揸車?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03693d0a2584f2bfacb47540e2fee9233618b39d","tid":1923824,"uid":209657,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:49:22.000Z","msg":"天花板遭刮爛 網民：一定係天花板襲擊警車<br />\n<br />\n昨晚11時許，警方一輛衝鋒車駛進鴨脷洲南灣停車場通道時，疑未有留意高度限制，警車車頂直撞天花板。網上圖片可見，該輛警車車頂緊貼天花板，天花板疑遭車輛刮花損毀，呈現長方型空洞，物料外露，白色零件半吊空中，碎片散落地面。肇事警車疑卡在該處，無法動彈，數名警員於警車附近處理事件。有網民留言笑稱，「一定係天花板襲擊部警車」、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「全靠警車仗義犧牲頂住個（嗰）天花板先至冇冧落嚟！」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2531793/org/23029a38c7dbd05897d79ee3f1432c0d.jpg/vtbPfdwztuprLq1ltfdp5bhx0hxliJ38DIXNaAyFzWg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2531793%2Forg%2F23029a38c7dbd05897d79ee3f1432c0d.jpg%2FvtbPfdwztuprLq1ltfdp5bhx0hxliJ38DIXNaAyFzWg&h=5b5144ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c7b29d1fa44b78d60559f42f448405d78f2b979","tid":1923824,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"好似old neww嚟？"},{"pid":"8ee1d03b0c6893d1c408d34706847f0b62882907","tid":1923824,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2531962/org/dc46e5e1dac724e3aea2c2ef089358f4.jpg/naooukrOTkw4C2ZaPo66TspwTvYxIIYK7hCKrO4Qiqw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2531962%2Forg%2Fdc46e5e1dac724e3aea2c2ef089358f4.jpg%2FnaooukrOTkw4C2ZaPo66TspwTvYxIIYK7hCKrO4Qiqw&h=e7326a23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入口處貼有高度限制提示<br />\n<br />\n記者今午到現場查看，發現停車場內原本「半天吊」的物料已不見，而停車場入口處則寫有高度限制提示牌，提醒限制為2.4米。<br />\n南灣位於南區鴨脷洲東部，外形以320米流線型帆船設計，其設計於2011年榮獲「香港最佳建築（高樓）」的「高度表揚獎」。南灣一共有9座，設施包括住客及訪客停車場。"},{"pid":"8fb655976c400ba00eecf30374d02e8407e6040b","tid":1923824,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c7b29d1fa44b78d60559f42f448405d78f2b979","tid":1923824,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"好似old neww嚟？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警方發言人表示，港島總區衝鋒隊人員昨晚約11時40分駕駛警車前往香港仔鴨脷洲海旁道處理案件，其間駛入鴨脷洲海旁道八號一停車場時，意外撞到該停車場的天花板。事件中無人受傷，列作「交通意外無人受傷」。警方已聯絡停車場負責人，正積極跟進事件。"},{"pid":"fb450f043f02e3560645a31503adfd8806542926","tid":1923824,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"要唔要對天花板tg放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28d8b855b331ba822b6f2d8a6d28a1da25d8229","tid":1923824,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fb655976c400ba00eecf30374d02e8407e6040b","tid":1923824,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c7b29d1fa44b78d60559f42f448405d78f2b979","tid":1923824,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"好似old neww嚟？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警方發言人表示，港島總區衝鋒隊人員昨晚約11時40分駕駛警車前往香港仔鴨脷洲海旁道處理案件，其間駛入鴨脷洲海旁道八號一停車場時，意外撞到該停車場的天花板。事件中無人受傷，列作「交通意外無人受傷」。警方已聯絡停車場負責人，正積極跟進事件。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:52:29.000Z","msg":"拉鳩停車場負責人告阻差辦公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbd548bab38ef4235845f6e0fd4b12589db2d6f","tid":1923824,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2531921/org/60616ee58ca0ae0830f9f7ad54ed3bd6.jpg/uGLimolkxInm1Jd1e4Ih6PPhbdKxxGVvDkIiuQ5CIrk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2531921%2Forg%2F60616ee58ca0ae0830f9f7ad54ed3bd6.jpg%2FuGLimolkxInm1Jd1e4Ih6PPhbdKxxGVvDkIiuQ5CIrk&h=13a4a48c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻查資料，以往亦曾有警車因未有留意高度限制惹禍！2015年8月，一輛警車駛出馬鞍山新港城時，疑亦因未有留意高度限制，天花板卡在該處，當時事件中未有造成損毀。<br />\n<br />\n另外，去年11月中旬，一輛貨車於高鐵西九龍站停車場位置，準備駛進落客區時，疑未收回吊臂，高度超出限制，貨車隨即撞向入口指示牌。去年12月底，同樣位置一輛城巴雙層巴士欲駛入上址，惟疑車身超出高度，直撞向指示牌。"},{"pid":"59da698383b15bf8df81d288f64935c0f330108b","tid":1923824,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:53:34.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce745267ad86a294aaf8031a32a5517d1488f92f","tid":1923824,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fb655976c400ba00eecf30374d02e8407e6040b","tid":1923824,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c7b29d1fa44b78d60559f42f448405d78f2b979","tid":1923824,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:50:23.000Z","